Features
    - 16 drum pads
    - works with midi device
    - presets
    - load sound into pad
    - repeater functionality
    - press pad to edit sound
        - vol, pitch, start/end sample, visual waveform
    - velocity sensitive
    - effects

Ideas
    - mode to arrange pads like a keyboards

Audio Engine tweaks
-   sound channel
    -   does voice have to be triggers here. Move trigger() to voice
    -   let audio channel accept a list of voices instead of just one
-   continuous voices
    -   instead of fixed voices. Allows for realtime changes to voices